creator: BH App Development Ltd
descriptionHtml:
The ART 12 Week Body Transformation is a health and fitness program designed by industry leading personal trainer Olly Foster. A program designed to get you moving, feeling and looking better by teaching you about effective nutritional and training principles.

This program will provide you with structure, accountability and support with a fortnightly review process to make sure appropriate changes are made to get the best out fo you.

Hundreds of people have already transformed their physiques and their lives with ART. Of course, there are countless fitness programmes on the market, so what makes this one different?

With the ART Programme you’ll eat tasty wholesome food, you’ll get a kick out of the training you do, and you’ll get the right support to help you go the distance. You’ll also get all the tools in your box to make this a life-long body transformation, not a temporary result. Whatever your start point, whatever your age, you can do it.

Who are you? Or maybe it’s better to ask, “What kind of person are you?”

Take a moment to think, and read these questions before you answer:

Are you tired of being unhealthy or overweight?

Do you want to feel good about yourself again and actually like what you see in the mirror?

Do you lack confidence, not just in the gym but also in your everyday life, and want to make positive changes to create a new mentality?

Have you tried several fitness programmes before and found they either didn’t address your needs or didn’t provide the results you wanted?

Are you confused with the amount of information available – and all the contradictions it contains?

Or are you someone who struggles to find the time and motivation to get in shape because of long work hours or family obligations?

So how about it? Did any of the above ring true? If you answered yes to any of the questions, I am certain I can help. I can help you make a positive change in your life that will boost your energy levels, burn off stubborn blubber, sculpt your physique and leave you feeling healthier, happier and more confident.

The ART Programme is not a gimmick or a quick fix – it’s a forever life changing transformation.
